.SH REMOTE REPOSITORY COLLECTION
\fBarachna collect \-\-repo\fR clones a git repository (via \fBgit clone \-\-depth 1\fR),
auto-detects project type, runs collection, and cleans up the temporary directory.
Requires git installed on the system.
.PP
Profile selection:
.TP
\fB\-\-profile python\fR
Strict mode: uses the specified profile from the remote repo's
.arachna.json. Exits with an error listing available profiles if not found.
.TP
\fB(no \-\-profile)\fR
Auto-select mode:
.br
1. If the repo has a profile with \fB"remote": true\fR, uses that one.
.br
2. Multiple \fBremote: true\fR profiles — exits with an error, asks for \fB\-\-profile\fR.
.br
3. No \fBremote: true\fR profiles — auto-detects via \fBdetect_presets()\fR.
.br
4. Fallback: \fB"full"\fR profile.
.PP
Mark a profile as default for remote collection:
.B "remote": true
in the profile configuration.
.SH PLUGINS
Plugins add language-specific features without adding dependencies to core.
Install via pip extras or the plugin manager.
.PP
Available plugins:
.TS
tab(;);
l l.
javascript;Tree-sitter structural diff for JavaScript
typescript;Tree-sitter structural diff for TypeScript
go;Tree-sitter structural diff for Go
tiktoken;Accurate token counting for OpenAI models
transformers;HuggingFace tokenizers
.TE
.PP
Install: \fBpip install arachna[javascript]\fR
.br
Or: \fBarachna plugins install javascript \-\-execute\fR
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
ARACHNA_CHARS_PER_TOKEN
Token estimation ratio (default: 4). Use 2.5 for Cyrillic, 1.5 for CJK.
.TP
ARACHNA_MAX_HASH_SIZE
Max file size in bytes for SHA256 hashing (default: 10485760).
.TP
ARACHNA_MAX_OUTPUT_SIZE
Max stdout size in bytes for sandbox commands (default: 10485760).
.TP
ARACHNA_MAX_WORKERS
Parallel file I/O workers (default: 1, sequential). Set to 4 for HDD/network drives.
.TP
ARACHNA_PRE_COMMAND_DELAY
Seconds to sleep between pre_commands (default: 0).
.TP
ARACHNA_PRESETS_TIMEOUT
Timeout in seconds for presets update HTTP fetch (default: 10).
.TP
ARACHNA_SAFE_TOKENIZERS
Comma-separated safe tokenizer modules (default: tiktoken,transformers).
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
Create a config with auto-detected profiles:
.RS
.B arachna init \-\-defaults
.RE
.PP
Collect all profiles:
.RS
.B arachna collect \-\-all
.RE
.PP
Collect from a remote repository:
.RS
.B arachna collect \-\-repo https://github.com/user/repo
.RE
.PP
Collect from a remote repository with strict profile:
.RS
.B arachna collect \-\-repo https://github.com/user/repo \-\-profile python
.RE
.PP
Profile your project — measure token savings:
.RS
.B arachna profile
.RE
.PP
Install JavaScript plugin:
.RS
.B arachna plugins install javascript \-\-execute
.RE
.PP
Create a snapshot and diff later:
.RS
.B arachna snapshot create \-\-profile full \-\-name baseline
.br
.I ... make changes ...
.br
.B arachna diff \-\-from baseline
.RE
.PP
Diff with line numbers:
.RS
.B arachna diff \-\-from baseline \-\-line\-numbers
.RE
.PP
Machine-readable manifest for AI agents:
.RS
.B arachna manifest \-\-json
.RE
.SH FILES
.TP
\fI.arachna.json\fR
Project configuration with profiles.
.TP
\fIarachna_context/\fR
Default output directory for collected files.
.TP
\fI.arachna/\fR
Content-addressable store for Watch snapshots (auto-gitignored).
